body_text:
@ebrevdo has looked at cusparse in tf.
It's not hard to add a way to get the GPU memory of a tensor, but it's likely to be inefficient because we'd need to sync the GPU stream before that memory was useful for anything, and using anything you computed using that memory would require another sync.
OTOH it's not that much C++ code to make tf ops to do exactly this thing you want.

